## Security

* Only users with permission:

```text
users.manage
```

can access this module.

* Use CSRF
* Validate email uniqueness
* Never display password hashes
* Prevent admin from deactivating their own account
* Use audit logs:

  * USER_CREATED
  * USER_UPDATED
  * USER_DEACTIVATED
  * USER_ACTIVATED
  * USER_ROLE_UPDATED

